# Patch notes for 145.0.219

These patch notes summarize the changes from version 144.0.155.

Added 11 new APIs:
* NptRecurrency.ValidateRecurringNpts (POST /api/data/npt/{taskId}/recurring/settings/validate)
* NptRecurrency.UpdateRecurringNpts (PUT /api/data/npt/{taskId}/recurring/settings)
* ProjectChargeCode.UpdateProjectChargeCode (PUT /api/data/projects/chargecodes/{chargeCodeId})
* ProjectChargeCode.DeleteProjectChargeCode (DELETE /api/data/projects/chargecodes/{chargeCodeId})
* ProjectFolder.CreateProjectFolder (POST /api/data/project-folders)
* ProjectFolder.UpdateProjectFolder (PUT /api/data/project-folders/{projectFolderId})
* ProjectFolder.DeleteProjectFolder (DELETE /api/data/project-folders/{projectFolderId})
* ProjectStatus.UpdateProjectStatus (PUT /api/data/projects/statuses/{projectStatusId})
* ProjectStatus.DeleteProjectStatus (DELETE /api/data/projects/statuses/{projectStatusId})
* TaskRecurrency.ValidateRecurringTasks (POST /api/data/tasks/{taskId}/recurring/settings/validate)
* TaskRecurrency.UpdateRecurringTasks (PUT /api/data/tasks/{taskId}/recurring/settings)

Renamed 5 old APIs:
* Renamed 'Timesheet.QueryTimeSheets' to 'Timesheet.QueryTimeEntries'
* Renamed 'Timesheet.ReturnsActiveAdminTasksThatAreUsedToReportTime' to 'Timesheet.RetrieveAdministrativeTasks'
* Renamed 'Timesheet.SubmitResourceTimeSheetForApproval' to 'Timesheet.SubmitTimeSheet'
* Renamed 'Timesheet.ApproveResourceTimeSheetApprovalRequest' to 'Timesheet.ApproveTimeSheet'
* Renamed 'Timesheet.RejectResourceTimeSheetApprovalRequest' to 'Timesheet.RejectTimeSheet'

Changes to data models:
* ProjectDto: Added new field `ownerId`
* TaskCreateDto: Added new field `index`


